{"type": "article", "id": 29441, "title": "玻璃家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-11T23:01:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712000352qdr0TJMEWNgQXZac.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>炎炎夏日，玻璃家具所特有的清爽感能够让人眼前一亮。意大利设计师 Cristina Celestino 领导的设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.designattico.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Attico</a> 最近就为玻璃家具制作商 <a href=\"http://www.tonellidesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tonelli Design</a> 设计了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.tonellidesign.com/eng/progettisti_dett.php?ID=120\" rel=\"nofollow\">Opalina</a> 的家具系列。Celestino 在设计时借鉴了 opaline 的概念，这个词语在 19 世纪之前指的是乳白色，后来逐渐用它同时来指代物品的颜色和材质。通过各种厚重玻璃之间巧妙的组合，Opalina 系列完全靠玻璃自身进行支撑，几乎看不到外部组件构成的结合，展现出了玻璃特有的光滑和剔透感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712000413Pd5ivnexYKLuJQCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712000412csiLCMUAzldoFZy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120004133vQwltoCBS6m8RN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712000413fjBED86hwqL4i9tM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}